{
  "stem": "17001.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We are worse off than any animal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because when you take in a dog, you take it in because you want to take care of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we were herded into this [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That we didn't see any future.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I said if this woman who had not be able to stand on her feet, and she wants to live.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I want to live to tell the world what is going on here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "What happening.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So that's why I'm really happy in a way that I had an opportunity to tell the honest, unfortunate, heartbreaking, painful story to you, which is really in a nutshell.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because when you were in Auschwitz, every minute was a year.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And every day was 10 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It got to the point where we were-- like couldn't even concentrate from the brom that we have taken in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In the very beginning, we were like zombies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We-- we couldn't think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "After suffering in the train and then in the ghetto, on the train, getting off, selecting every day, every day, nighttime.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it got to the point already where we were hoping for a real miracle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said-- we were always looking up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said, God, if we are the chosen people, why do you let us suffer?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why do we have to go through all this?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is worse than hell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hell must be wonderful comparing to this place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So one day, like towards middle of or beginning of November, we had heard a big bust.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The big blow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But meantime, we had seen some airplanes flying by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were always hoping they would throw a bomb and then it would finish us, because it was just unbearable by that time.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
